plot: Inspired by the work of Alfred Hitchcock, this third "sequel" to Edward D. Wood's "Plan Nine from Outer Space" continues to follow the misadventures of Regis Stanely, Dr. Clayburgh and Bela, the space vampire.
title: Plan 12: The Ultimate Conflict
